00:34:11,550 --> 00:34:13,340
Shaping titanium alloy

891
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,740
into custom forms

892
00:34:15,070 --> 00:34:16,860
takes extremely high-end machining.

893
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:18,380
Especially the sample slot.

894
00:34:18,670 --> 00:34:20,380
Only CNC machines can do it.

895
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:21,090
But CNC machines

896
00:34:21,110 --> 00:34:22,090
are most likely imported.

897
00:34:22,710 --> 00:34:23,940
Large imported machinery.

898
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:26,050
Which company imported it?

899
00:34:26,280 --> 00:34:27,170
What's its purpose?

900
00:34:27,190 --> 00:34:28,090
Who received it?

901
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:29,340
When was it imported?

902
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:31,570
Customs records all of that.

903
00:34:31,590 --> 00:34:32,530
We can just check it.

904
00:34:33,030 --> 00:34:33,860
We checked,

905
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:34,780
and we found it.

906
00:34:35,710 --> 00:34:37,170
Among those importing companies,

907
00:34:37,190 --> 00:34:37,780
large companies

908
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:38,340
would never take

909
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:39,820
unknown orders like this.

910
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:40,420
So,

911
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:41,860
we screened

912
00:34:41,880 --> 00:34:43,420
small firms and those

913
00:34:43,440 --> 00:34:44,260
in liquidation.

914
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:46,050
Finally locked onto one factory

915
00:34:46,520 --> 00:34:48,420
that can make
this kind of layered thermos.

916
00:34:48,480 --> 00:34:49,780
Yongding Manufacturing.

917
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:51,210
But the boss of Yongding

918
00:34:51,230 --> 00:34:53,010
[Yongding]
insisted he never took such orders.

919
00:34:53,030 --> 00:34:53,820
[Yongding]
And

920
00:34:53,820 --> 00:34:54,630
[Yongding]

921
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:55,820
we have no solid evidence

922
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:58,050
proving they actually produced it.

923
00:34:58,070 --> 00:34:59,210
So the case is stalled.

924
00:35:00,480 --> 00:35:01,570
Time is money.

925
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:18,090
Mentor.

926
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:20,490
What are you doing?

927
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:22,300
Aren't you heading to Yongding?

928
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:24,300
What Yongding?

929
00:35:24,360 --> 00:35:25,210
I'm going home.

930
00:35:25,230 --> 00:35:26,980
I know you too well.

931
00:35:27,040 --> 00:35:29,090
Just now, Shihuo said, "Time is money."

932
00:35:29,110 --> 00:35:30,780
And I could tell you're tempted.

933
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:31,980
Mentor,

934
00:35:32,150 --> 00:35:34,460
this thermos is likely tied to Group E.

935
00:35:34,880 --> 00:35:36,090
Just let me go.

936
00:35:36,110 --> 00:35:37,570
Maybe I can help.

937
00:35:38,030 --> 00:35:39,650
Last time with Qian Shengkai,

938
00:35:39,670 --> 00:35:41,170
we worked pretty well together,
didn't we?

939
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:43,570
Get in.

940
00:35:43,590 --> 00:35:44,090
Got it!

941
00:35:58,590 --> 00:35:59,380
This is it.

942
00:35:59,380 --> 00:36:00,560
[Hakka Rice Rolls]

943
00:36:08,230 --> 00:36:08,570
Zip it

944
00:36:08,590 --> 00:36:09,300
if anyone asks.

945
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:10,300
Especially Zhang Dayu.

946
00:36:10,590 --> 00:36:12,050
You've said that all along.

947
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:13,460
We're not here to investigate,

948
00:36:13,520 --> 00:36:15,090
and we don't have the authority.

949
00:36:15,110 --> 00:36:16,980
We're just here
to practice reading people.

950
00:36:17,150 --> 00:36:18,090
You're my trainee.

951
00:36:18,110 --> 00:36:18,900
I've got to protect you

952
00:36:19,190 --> 00:36:20,380
and can't let you break the rules.

953
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:22,740
I'm so touched.

954
00:36:23,800 --> 00:36:25,570
So how are you
planning to check this out?

955
00:36:25,710 --> 00:36:26,340
No idea.

956
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:28,300
We can't approach directly.

957
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:29,420
Let's wait and see.

958
00:36:38,040 --> 00:36:39,130
What would you like?

959
00:36:39,550 --> 00:36:40,130
Two bowls of wontons,

960
00:36:40,150 --> 00:36:40,610
thanks.

961
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:41,130
Alright,

962
00:36:41,150 --> 00:36:41,940
have a seat.

963
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:42,420
It's fine.

964
00:36:45,360 --> 00:36:45,780
Ma'am,

965
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:47,010
I have a question.

966
00:36:47,320 --> 00:36:49,940
Are you familiar
with Yongding Manufacturing?

967
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:51,380
You're here to collect debts?

968
00:36:51,630 --> 00:36:52,690
No,

969
00:36:52,710 --> 00:36:54,300
we do group insurance

970
00:36:54,360 --> 00:36:55,940
for factories,

971
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:57,860
companies, that kind of thing.

972
00:36:58,320 --> 00:36:59,460
We're just passing by.

973
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:00,340
Thought we'd ask.

974
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:02,900
Yongding hasn't been doing well lately.

975
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:04,900
More debt collectors

976
00:37:04,960 --> 00:37:06,170
than workers these days.

977
00:37:06,520 --> 00:37:08,260
Better try Zhaofeng across the street.

978
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:09,260
They're doing okay.

979
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:13,090
See? Those guys
are here collecting debts.

980
00:37:13,110 --> 00:37:15,130
They've been waiting here for a week.

981
00:37:15,520 --> 00:37:17,650
Bro, let's order something to drink.

982
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:19,050
Drink what?

983
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:20,010
If we don't collect,

984
00:37:20,230 --> 00:37:21,300
